\(f_x(1,2)\) \{ans_rule(30)\}
$PAR
\(f_y(1,2)\) \{ans_rule(30)\}
$PAR
\(f_x(-2,-2)\) \{ans_rule(30)\}
$PAR
\(f_y(-2,-2)\) \{ans_rule(30)\}

END_TEXT
